      "content": "## 1) STRUCTURE ANALYSIS (what\u2019s in the molecule)\n**SMILES:** `CCOc1ccccc1OCC[NH2+][C@H](C)Cc1ccc(OC)c(S(N)(=O)=O)c1`",
